  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with persistent asthma

          -  Asthma treatment for at least 12 months

          -  Regular visitors of the participating community pharmacy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe co-morbidity

          -  &gt; 10 pack-years smoking history

          -  Asthma Control Test score &lt; 15 or =25
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
